    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>basmati rice</strong>, <strong>half </strong>of your <strong>ground turmeric </strong>and 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> to a pot with a lid and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once cooked, remove from the heat and keep covered until serving</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/amritsari-basa-fry-with-kachumber-and-rice/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong>, <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>and a squeeze of your <strong>lemon </strong>to a bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>marinated basa</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/amritsari-basa-fry-with-kachumber-and-rice/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>gram flour</strong>, <strong>ground paprika</strong>, <strong>garam masala </strong>and the <strong>remaining ground turmeric </strong>to a plate with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and mix it all together</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/amritsari-basa-fry-with-kachumber-and-rice/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>marinated basa </strong>to the plate and press it into the flour mixture until it is fully coated \u2013 this is your <strong>coated basa</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/amritsari-basa-fry-with-kachumber-and-rice/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated basa</strong> and cook for 3-4 min on each side, or until nicely golden and crisp \u2013 this is your <strong>Amritsari basa fry</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/amritsari-basa-fry-with-kachumber-and-rice/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Dice your <strong>cucumber</strong> finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Slice <strong>half</strong> your <strong>green chilli[es]</strong> into rounds and finely chop the remaining</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/amritsari-basa-fry-with-kachumber-and-rice/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>diced cucumber</strong>, <strong>chopped tomato</strong>, <strong>sliced shallot </strong>and <strong>chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to a bowl</p><p>Add a squeeze of <strong>lemon</strong> juice, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>kachumber salad</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/amritsari-basa-fry-with-kachumber-and-rice/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p><p>Serve the <strong>Amritsari basa fry </strong>with the <strong>kachumber salad</strong>, <strong>mint & coriander chutney </strong>and <strong>turmeric rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chilli rounds </strong>and a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
